            "title": "印度總理莫迪將開啟日本訪問行程 據悉將達成投資和供應協議",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"印度總理莫迪將開啟日本訪問行程 據悉將達成投資和供應協議\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rLpuI.viVNglVmK5X_1a0g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-08/010d22c0-847a-11f0-bf39-2415e7323d0c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">印度總理莫迪將開啟日本訪問行程 據悉將達成投資和供應協議</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
