            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"字節估值有望突破2.5萬億\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"686\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wd8K6hY4bXt9JyY30ZjCpg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NjtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-08/06e0cc30-846e-11f0-bead-730b3d5e245d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">字節估值有望突破2.5萬億</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
